# Release archives (DMG + appcast) — hosted on the site, not committed
dist/
# `**/` needed since these patterns have a slash in the middle — without it git anchors
# them to the repo root only (per gitignore's own rule), missing nested copies like
# Tests/KouenRobotTests/graphify-out/cache/.
**/graphify-out/cache/
**/graphify-out/GRAPH_TREE.html
# Dated graphify snapshot dirs (e.g. graphify-out/2026-06-10/) — duplicates of graph.json
**/graphify-out/20*/
# Large regenerated artifacts (20MB+ graph.json, 1.9MB graph.html) — GRAPH_SUMMARY.md/
# GRAPH_REPORT.md stay tracked as the human-readable index; these two don't need git history.
**/graphify-out/graph.json
**/graphify-out/graph.html
# Wiki export (15MB+, thousands of files) regenerated by `graphify update .` — same
# bloat class as graph.json/graph.html above, just regenerable markdown, not source.
**/graphify-out/wiki/
# Per-run hook log, overwritten every commit — not useful in history.
**/graphify-out/.last-refresh.log
.robot-output/
# Robot Framework's own default output location/names (run from the repo root or Tests/)
/log.html
/output.xml
/report.html
/results/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Shared agent protocol (symlinked)
.ai/

# Agent-task worktrees (P32) — sandboxes, not source
.kouen-worktrees/
